subject: Tennis
lead_paragraph: Maria Sharapova pulled out of the Italian Open semifinals in Rome because of a strained left calf. In Sunday’s final, Jelena Jankovic will meet Alize Cornet, a qualifier who defeated Anna Chakvetadze, 3-6, 6-4, 6-3.
